data.name: Chat_Rebel_AboutPower2
data.value: Those solar panels need a power kickstart so they can realign and begin supplying energy.

data.name: Chat_Rebel_AboutPower3
data.value: There are some components in this container. Sending coordinates.

data.name: Chat_Rebel_Intro1
data.value: Welcome to our former settlement, there used to be over a hundred of us living here, working and trying to build a new colony, we thought the R.O.S. contract would be the start of a new era, growing into something even bigger.

data.name: Chat_Rebel_Intro2
data.value: Shortly after the artefact was excavated they sent their gunships, mercilessly slaughtered almost all of us and left the colony in ruins as you see before you.

data.name: Chat_Rebel_Intro3
data.value: The reason we have brought you here is to ask for your help, we cannot strike at the corporation alone but with your engineering skills we might have a chance, there is an old frigate in the hangar here, it was damaged in the attack but with your abilities I'm sure you will be able to get it flying again.

data.name: Chat_Rebel_Intro4
data.value: We are planning an assault on the corporation fleet and need every ship we can get.

data.name: Chat_Rebel_Outro1
data.value: We did it! They are retreating!

data.name: Chat_Rebel_Outro2
data.value: Finally those bastards have a taste of the suffering they inflicted on us!

data.name: Chat_Rebel_Outro3
data.value: We couldn't have done it without you but it's not over yet, we still need to take the artefact from them, it mustn't be allowed to remain in the hands of people who would use its secrets for their own egomaniacal ends.

data.name: Chat_VA_AboutPower1
data.value: I'm not detecting any power signatures from the base.
